Please read @overview.md for a high-level overview of the project before answering.

### How to Test:
- Run "make test" for the usual test suite
- Run "make debug-render" to test rendering, it will delete the old screenshot and take a new one

Avoid the following unless there is no other way:
- Calling pytest directly
- Running the program using uv directly
- Using rm